@Help Phone
#end
:touch
#take torches 1 tp
/i
#if vamp then hint
$
Hi, this is Help Phone! Did you know that
the bouncer with the coat hanger from the
Broken Aorta has a super-sensitive nose?
It's true! Anything that smells, well,
sour or just generally funky will probably
do weird stuff to him... nice talking to
you!
$
#end
:hint
$
Hi, this is Help Phone! It's sort of
interesting... did you know that a vacuum
tube, one of the major ingredients in
Dr. Hudson's revolutionary supergas, is
commonly used in TV sets?
Nice talking to you...
$
#end
:tp
$
Sorry, it looks like you won't have enough
time to act on our advice anyway...
$
#end

