@Helpful Man
#end
:touch
#zap touch
$
Hey kid, check this phone out!
$
$... wow. It's got buttons and everything.
$
No no! This is the Help Phone! Just dial
it up and you'll get a clue about the
current level!
$
$Well, that's got to be handy.
$
Yeah... only there's a hitch. Every time
you call, you'll eat up one minute of the
time you have left. So only call if you're
sure you need the help!
$
$I'll be careful.
$
You'll be dead!
$
$Huh?
$
Sorry. Don't know what came over me...
$
#end
:touch
MAN: Don't talk to me! The phone!
#end

